description: Stunning 2 Bedroom plus study in an elevatored building, private outdoor space and garage parking! Sunlight floods this unit with 20 windows on the 3rd floor of this professionally managed building. The unit offers a beautifully designed open concept floor plan encompassing the entire 3rd floor. The Leicht kitchen includes top of the line Thermador appliances, quartz countertops, large quartz waterfall island and custom cabinetry. Hardwood floors throughout. The living room centerpiece includes a 48" gas fireplace with a granite accent. Big open living room provides plenty of space for entertaining. High ceilings with built in audio and recessed lighting. Master bedroom has 3 large windows, a large walk in closet and adjoining bath with a rainfall shower and double vanity. Second bedroom has 2 large windows and a big closet. Modern second bath off hallway. Add’l room can be used as an office/small study. Fabulous location. Photos are virtually staged.
